  "prompt": "Which is the best training institute for spoken English in Pune?",
  "response": "Deciding on the best training institute for spoken English in Pune can be subjective, as it depends on individual preferences, learning styles, and specific needs. However, some of the popular and highly-rated institutes known for their spoken English programs in Pune include:\n\n1. **British Council**: Known for its high-quality courses and experienced faculty, the British Council offers a range of English language courses including spoken English.\n\n2. **Symbiosis Institute of Foreign and Indian Languages (SIFIL)**: Symbiosis is a reputed name in education, and their language programs are well-regarded.\n\n3. **Let\u2019s Talk Institute**: Known for its practical approach and personalized training, Let's Talk Institute offers various levels of spoken English courses.\n\n4. **Bharat Institute of Spoken English**: Offers comprehensive courses aimed at improving fluency and confidence in spoken English.\n\n5. **Inlingua**: Part of a global network, Inlingua offers effective spoken English training with a focus on interactive learning.\n\n6. **English Language Teaching Institute of Symbiosis (ELTIS)**: Offers specialized courses in spoken English and has a good reputation in Pune.\n\n7. **Cambridge Institute**: Offers a wide range of English language courses including spoken English, and is known for its certified trainers.\n\nBefore enrolling, it is advisable to visit the institutes, talk to the trainers, and possibly attend demo classes to ensure the teaching methodology and environment suit your learning preferences.",
